{"id": 3, "lang": "zu", "domain": "civic_affairs", "text": "Ekhuluma emhlanganweni womphakathi eSoweto, abaholi bomphakathi kanye nomasipala baxoxisane ngezinkinga ezibhekene nezinsiza zomphakathi ezifana nokuntuleka kwamanzi nokulibaziseka kokuqoqwa kukadoti. Abantu abebekhona baveze ukukhathazeka ngokuthi lezi zinkinga zihlala isikhathi eside ngaphandle kokuxazululwa okucacile. Umasipala uthe kunezinhlelo ezisasebenza zokuthuthukisa ukusebenza kwamasevisi ngokwengeza abasebenzi kanye nemishini emisha. Abahlali baceliwe ukuba babike izinkinga ngokushesha ukuze kube lula ukungenelela. Uhulumeni uthi ukubambisana nomphakathi kubalulekile ukuze kuthuthukiswe izinga lokuhlinzekwa kwezinsiza. Le ngxoxo ibhekwa njengengxenye ebalulekile yokwakha ukwethembana phakathi kukahulumeni nabantu."}
{"id": 4, "lang": "zu", "domain": "government", "text": "Ngemuva komhlangano kazwelonke ePitoli, uhulumeni umemezele uhlelo olusha lokulwa nokuntuleka kwemisebenzi ngokugxila ekuthuthukiseni amabhizinisi amancane naphakathi. Lolu hlelo luhlose ukuhlinzeka ngosizo lwezimali kanye nokuqeqeshwa kosomabhizinisi abasha ukuze bakwazi ukukhulisa imisebenzi yabo. Izikhulu zithi kuzokwakhiwa izikhungo zokweseka amabhizinisi ezindaweni ezahlukene ukuze kube lula ukufinyelela usizo. Abahlanganyeli bamukele le nqubomgomo kodwa bacele ukuthi kube nokulandelela okuqinile ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukusebenza kwayo. Uhulumeni uthi lokhu kuyingxenye yesu elibanzi lokukhuthaza ukukhula komnotho okusimeme ezweni lonke."}
{"id": 5, "lang": "zu", "domain": "municipal_services", "text": "Umasipala waseThekwini ubike ukuthi kuzoqaliswa uhlelo olusha lokuthuthukisa ukuhlinzekwa kwamanzi ezindaweni ezihlala zibhekene nokushoda kwamanzi ngesikhathi sasehlobo. Lolu hlelo luhlanganisa ukwakhiwa kwamathangi amasha nokulungiswa kwemibhobho emidala. Izisebenzi zikamasipala zithi seziqalile ukuhlola izindawo ezisengozini enkulu ukuze kubekwe phambili ukungenelela. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuthi babambe iqhaza ekongeni amanzi ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukusimama kwalesi simo. Uhulumeni wasekhaya uthi uzosebenzisa izinhlelo zokwazisa umphakathi ukuze abantu baqonde kangcono indlela yokuphatha amanzi. Le projekthi kulindeleke ukuthi ithuthukise kakhulu ukuzinza kokuhlinzekwa kwamanzi esifundeni."}
{"id": 6, "lang": "zu", "domain": "public_policy", "text": "Uhulumeni wesifundazwe umemezele izinguquko ezintsha kumigomo yokuhanjiswa kwezinsiza zomphakathi ukuze kuncishiswe ukubambezeleka ekuphenduleni izikhalazo zabantu. Lolu shintsho luhlose ukwenza kube lula ukulandelela izikhalo kusetshenziswa izinhlelo zedijithali. Izikhulu zithi lokhu kuzokwandisa ukubeka obala kanye nokuthuthukisa ukuphendula ngokushesha. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuthi basebenzise lezi zinhlelo ezintsha ukuze babike izinkinga ezikhona emiphakathini yabo. Uhulumeni uthi le ndlela izosiza ekwakheni izinsiza zomphakathi ezisebenza kahle futhi ezithembekile."}
{"id": 7, "lang": "zu", "domain": "agriculture", "text": "Emapulazini aseFree State abalimi babhekene nezinselelo zokwehla kwesivuno ngenxa yokushintsha kwesimo sezulu kanye nokuntuleka kwemvula eyanele. Uhulumeni uthi useqalile uhlelo lokweseka abalimi ngokuhlinzeka ngembewu ethuthukisiwe kanye nokuqeqeshwa kwezindlela zokulima ezisimeme. Lezi zinhlelo zihlose ukwandisa ukukhiqizwa kokudla nokunciphisa ukuthembela ekungenisweni kokudla kwamanye amazwe. Abalimi bakhuthazwa ukuthi basebenzise izindlela zesimanje zokonga amanzi nokuvikela umhlabathi. Uhulumeni uthi uzosebenzisana nezinhlangano zezolimo ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuthi abalimi abancane nabo bayazuza kulezi zinhlelo."}
{"id": 8, "lang": "zu", "domain": "rural_development", "text": "Ezindaweni zasemakhaya aseKwaZulu-Natali kuqale uhlelo olusha lokuthuthukisa ingqalasizinda yezolimo kanye nokufinyelela ezimakethe kubalimi abancane. Lolu hlelo luhlose ukwakha imigwaqo yokuxhuma amapulazi nezikhungo zokuhweba ukuze kube lula ukuthutha imikhiqizo. Izikhulu zithi lokhu kuzokwandisa amathuba emisebenzi futhi kuthuthukise umnotho wasezindaweni zasemakhaya. Abaholi bomphakathi bamukele le projekthi kodwa bacele ukuthi kuqinisekiswe ukuthi iyafinyelela kubo bonke abalimi ngaphandle kokukhetha. Uhulumeni uthi uzosebenzisana nezinhlaka zendawo ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuqaliswa okuphumelelayo kwalolu hlelo."}
{"id": 9, "lang": "zu", "domain": "agriculture", "text": "Ngemuva kokwanda kwesidingo sokudla ezweni, uhulumeni umemezele uhlelo lokweseka abalimi bommbila ngokuhlinzeka ngosizo lwezimali kanye nemishini yokulima. Lolu hlelo luhlose ukukhulisa ukukhiqizwa kokudla okuyisisekelo ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuphepha kokudla ezweni. Abalimi bazophinde bathole ukuqeqeshwa mayelana nokusebenzisa imbewu ethuthukisiwe kanye nokulawula izinambuzane ngendlela efanele. Izikhulu zithi lokhu kuyingxenye yesu elibanzi lokuqinisa umnotho wezolimo. Abahlanganyeli emkhakheni wezolimo bakubonge lokhu kodwa bacele ukuthi kube nokubeka iso okuqinile ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukusatshalaliswa okufanele kwezinsiza."}
{"id": 10, "lang": "zu", "domain": "rural_development", "text": "Emiphakathini yasemakhaya aseMpumalanga Kapa kuqalwe uhlelo lokuthuthukisa ukufinyelela emanzini okuhlanzekile kanye nezinsiza zokunisela emapulazini amancane. Lolu hlelo luhlose ukunciphisa ubunzima ababhekene nabo abalimi ngesikhathi sezomiso ezinde. Izisebenzi zikahulumeni zithi seziqalile ukufaka amapayipi amasha kanye nokulungisa imithombo yamanzi endala. Abalimi bakhuthazwa ukuba basebenzise lezi zinsiza ngendlela esimeme ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukusimama kwesikhathi eside. Uhulumeni uthi le projekthi izodlala indima enkulu ekuthuthukiseni ukukhiqizwa kokudla ezindaweni zasemakhaya."}
{"id": 1, "lang": "zu", "domain": "social_grants", "text": "Abantu abangaphezu kwezigidi ezintathu ezweni lonke sebezuze ezinhlelweni ezintsha zokukhokhwa kwezibonelelo zikahulumeni ezibhekiswe emindenini esengozini enkulu. Uhulumeni uthi le nkqubo ihlose ukuqinisekisa ukuthi abantu abadala, izingane kanye nabakhubazekile bathola ukwesekwa okufanele ngesikhathi. Izikhulu zomnyango wezenhlalakahle zithi izinhlelo zokukhokha sezithuthukisiwe ukuze kuncishiswe ukubambezeleka nokwandisa ukufinyelela kwabahlomulayo. Abahlomulayo bakhuthazwa ukuthi basebenzise izindlela ezisemthethweni zokubhalisa ukuze bagweme ukukhwabanisa. Uhulumeni uthi lokhu kuyingxenye yomzamo wokunciphisa ubuphofu nokwakha imiphakathi ezinzile. Abaholi bomphakathi bamnkele kahle lo msebenzi kodwa bacele ukuthi kube nokubeka iso okuqinile ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuthi akekho oshiywa ngaphandle."}
{"id": 2, "lang": "zu", "domain": "housing_support", "text": "Ngaphezulu kwemindeni eyizinkulungwane ezinhlanu esifundeni saseGauteng izothola izindlu ezintsha ngaphansi kohlelo lukahulumeni lokwakhiwa kwezindlu zomphakathi. Lolu hlelo luhlose ukubhekana nenkinga yokushoda kwezindlu eziphephile nezingabizi kubantu abahola kancane. Izikhulu zithi izindlu ezakhiwayo zihambisana nezindinganiso zokuphepha kanye nengqalasizinda eyisisekelo efana namanzi nogesi. Abahlali abahlomulayo bakhuthazwa ukuthi babhalise ngokusemthethweni ukuze bakwazi ukufinyelela kulolu hlelo. Uhulumeni uthi uzosebenzisana nemikhandlu yendawo ukuqinisekisa ukuthi ukwabiwa kwezindlu kwenziwa ngendlela efanele. Abaholi bomphakathi bacele ukuthi kube sobala ekukhethweni kwabahlomulayo ukuze kugwenywe ukungqubuzana."}
{"id": 3, "lang": "zu", "domain": "community_welfare", "text": "Emiphakathini eminingi yasemadolobheni kuqale uhlelo olusha lokweseka imindeni ebhekene nobunzima bokungasebenzi kanye nokushoda kokudla. Lolu hlelo luhlanganisa ukuhlinzekwa ngamaphakethe okudla kanye nezinhlelo zokuqeqeshwa kwamakhono ukuze abantu bakwazi ukuzimela. Izisebenzi zenhlalakahle zithi ziyasebenzisana nezinhlangano ezizimele ukuze kwandiswe ukufinyelela kosizo. Abahlali abahlomulayo bakhuthazwa ukuthi babambe iqhaza ezinhlelweni zokuqeqeshwa ukuze bathuthukise amathuba abo emisebenzi. Uhulumeni uthi lokhu kuyingxenye yesu elibanzi lokulwa nobuphofu emiphakathini esengozini enkulu. Abaholi bomphakathi bamnkele lolu hlelo kodwa bagcizelela isidingo sokuqhubeka nokwesekwa isikhathi eside."}
{"id": 4, "lang": "zu", "domain": "social_grants", "text": "Ekhuluma emhlanganweni wokwazisa umphakathi, izikhulu zikahulumeni zichaze izinguquko ezintsha ezinhlelweni zezibonelelo ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuthi abantu abafanelekile bathola usizo ngaphandle kokubambezeleka. Lolu hlelo olusha lusebenzisa izinhlelo zedijithali ukuqinisekisa ukubhaliswa okunembile nokunciphisa ukukhwabanisa. Abahlomulayo bakhuthazwa ukuthi bavuselele imininingwane yabo njalo ukuze bagweme ukuphazamiseka ekukhokhelweni. Uhulumeni uthi uzosebenzisana nezikhungo zomphakathi ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukufinyelela okulula kosizo. Abaholi bomphakathi bagcizelele ukubaluleka kokubeka iso ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuthi izinsiza zifinyelela kubantu abahlosiwe kuphela."}
{"id": 5, "lang": "zu", "domain": "housing_support", "text": "Umasipala waseThekwini umemezele uhlelo lokuphuthumisa ukwakhiwa kwezindlu kubantu abahlala ezindaweni ezingaphephile nezibizwa ngokuthi izindawo ezingahlelekile. Lolu hlelo luhlose ukuthutha imindeni iye ezindlini ezakhiwe ngokusemthethweni ezinezinsiza eziyisisekelo. Izisebenzi zikamasipala zithi seziqalile ukuhlonza izindawo ezibeka abantu engcupheni yezikhukhula kanye nokulimala. Abahlali baceliwe ukuthi basebenzisane nohulumeni ngesikhathi sokuthuthwa ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuphepha. Uhulumeni uthi lokhu kuyingxenye yomzamo wokwakha imiphakathi ehlala kahle nenokuphepha. Abaholi bomphakathi bacele ukuthi kube nokuxhumana okucacile ukuze kugwenywe ukudideka ngesikhathi sokuthuthwa."}
{"id": 6, "lang": "zu", "domain": "community_welfare", "text": "Ngemuva kokwanda kwezinkinga zokungasebenzi emiphakathini ethile, uhulumeni umemezele uhlelo lokweseka abantu abasha ngemisebenzi yesikhashana kanye nokuqeqeshwa kwamakhono. Lolu hlelo luhlose ukunciphisa umthelela wobuphofu ngokunikeza abantu amathuba okusebenza ezinhlelweni zomphakathi. Izikhulu zithi izinkampani ezizimele nazo zizobamba iqhaza ekwakheni amathuba emisebenzi. Abahlomulayo bakhuthazwa ukuthi basebenzise leli thuba ukuthuthukisa amakhono abo. Uhulumeni uthi lokhu kuyingxenye yesu elibanzi lokwakha umnotho onamathuba alinganayo kubo bonke."}
{"id": 7, "lang": "zu", "domain": "social_grants", "text": "Izinkulungwane zabantu abadala ezweni lonke zizothola ukwenyuswa kwezibonelelo zazo kulandela isimemezelo sikahulumeni esisha esihlose ukulwa nokukhuphuka kwezindleko zokuphila. Izikhulu zithi lokhu kukhuphuka kuhloswe ukusiza abantu abadala ukuba bakwazi ukuhlangabezana nezidingo zabo eziyisisekelo. Uhlelo lokukhokha luzoqhubeka ngendlela ejwayelekile kodwa luthuthukiswe ukuze kuncishiswe ukubambezeleka. Abahlomulayo bakhuthazwa ukuthi basebenzise iziteshi ezisemthethweni ukuze bathole ulwazi oluqondile. Uhulumeni uthi uzibophezele ekuqinisekiseni ukuthi izakhamuzi ezisengozini enkulu azishiywa ngaphandle kosizo."}
{"id": 8, "lang": "zu", "domain": "housing_support", "text": "Emiphakathini yasemakhaya kuqale uhlelo lokwakhiwa kwezindlu ezibhekele imindeni ehola kancane ukuze kuthuthukiswe izinga lokuphila. Lolu hlelo luhlanganisa ukwakhiwa kwezindlu ezinamandla ezingamelana nezimo zezulu ezinzima. Izikhulu zithi izindawo ezikhethiwe zisebenza ngokuhambisana nezinhlelo zentuthuko yesifunda. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuthi babambe iqhaza ezinhlelweni zokubhalisa ukuze bakwazi ukufakwa ohlwini lwabahlomulayo. Uhulumeni uthi lokhu kuyingxenye yokuzibophezela ekwakheni imiphakathi ephephile nenokulingana. Abaholi bomphakathi bagcizelele ukubaluleka kokuba sobala ekukhethweni kwabahlomulayo."}
{"id": 9, "lang": "zu", "domain": "community_welfare", "text": "Ngaphakathi kwezinhlelo ezintsha zokweseka imiphakathi esengozini, uhulumeni usungule izikhungo zosizo ezizohlinzeka ngokudla, izeluleko kanye nokwesekwa kwezempilo kubantu abaswele. Lezi zikhungo ziqale ukusebenza ezindaweni ezithile ezihlushwa izinga eliphezulu lobuphofu. Izisebenzi zithi inhloso enkulu ukunciphisa umthelela wokungalingani emphakathini. Abahlomulayo bakhuthazwa ukuthi basebenzise lezi zinsiza ukuze bathuthukise izimpilo zabo. Uhulumeni uthi uzosebenzisana nezinhlangano zomphakathi ukuqinisekisa ukusimama kwalezi zinhlelo zesikhathi eside."}
{"id": 1, "lang": "zu", "domain": "education", "text": "Ngaphezulu kwabafundi abayizinkulungwane eziyishumi ezikoleni ezahlukene esifundazweni saseGauteng bathole ithuba lokuqala uhlelo olusha lokuthuthukisa ukufunda olugxile ekuthuthukiseni amakhono ezibalo, ukufunda nokubhala kanye nokucabanga okujulile. Uhulumeni uthi lolu hlelo luhlose ukunciphisa izinga eliphezulu lokwehluleka ezikoleni ngokunikeza othisha ukwesekwa okukhulu kanye nezinsiza ezengeziwe zokufundisa. Izikole eziningi sezithole izincwadi ezintsha, amathuluzi okufundisa kanye nezinhlelo zokuqeqesha othisha ukuze bathuthukise indlela yokufundisa. Abazali bakhuthazwa ukuthi babambe iqhaza ekufundeni kwezingane zabo ngokubambisana nothisha ukuze kuthuthukiswe imiphumela yezemfundo. Izikhulu zemfundo zithi lokhu kuyingxenye yesu elibanzi lokwakha isizukulwane esinamakhono aqinile okuzimela. Abafundi nabo bakhuthazwa ukuthi basebenzise amathuba okuqeqeshwa angeziwe ukuze bathuthukise ikusasa labo futhi babe nempumelelo emkhakheni abawukhethayo."}
{"id": 2, "lang": "zu", "domain": "education", "text": "Ezinhlanganweni zemfundo ephakeme ezweni lonke kuqale uhlelo olusha lokweseka abafundi abasuka emiphakathini esengozini ngokubanikeza izibonelelo zokufunda kanye nokusekelwa kwezindlu. Uhulumeni uthi le ndlela ihlose ukuqinisekisa ukuthi akukho mfundi oshiywa ngaphandle ngenxa yezimo zezimali. Izinhlangano zemfundo ephakeme zisebenzisana nohulumeni ukuhlinzeka ngezinhlelo zokuqeqesha ezihambisana nezidingo zomnotho wanamuhla. Abafundi bakhuthazwa ukuthi basebenzise izinsiza zokwelulekwa ukuze bakwazi ukuphumelela ezifundweni zabo. Izikhulu zithi lokhu kuyingxenye yokwakha umnotho onolwazi oluqinile noluncintisanayo. Abaholi bezemfundo baphinde bagcizelela ukubaluleka kokuthuthukisa izinga lokuphumelela kwabafundi ukuze kuqinisekiswe ikusasa eliqhakazile."}
{"id": 3, "lang": "zu", "domain": "education", "text": "Ngemuva kokukhula kokukhathazeka ngezinga lokuphumelela kwabafundi ezifundweni zezibalo nesayensi, uhulumeni umemezele uhlelo lokuqinisa ukufundisa lezi zifundo ezikoleni ezisemadolobheni nasezindaweni zasemakhaya. Lolu hlelo luhlanganisa ukuqeqeshwa okusha kothisha kanye nokwethulwa kwezinsiza zesimanje zokufundisa. Izikole ezithile sezithole amalabhorethri amasha ukuze abafundi bakwazi ukwenza izivivinyo ezisebenzayo. Abazali nabafundi bakhuthazwa ukuba basebenzisane nothisha ukuze kuthuthukiswe imiphumela. Uhulumeni uthi le ndlela izosiza ekwakheni isizukulwane esinamakhono esingaqhuba umnotho wezwe. Abaholi bomphakathi bakubheke njengokutshalwa kwemali okubalulekile ekusaseni lezwe."}
{"id": 4, "lang": "zu", "domain": "education", "text": "Ekhuluma emcimbini wokwethulwa kohlelo lwezemfundo, isikhulu sikahulumeni sichaze izinhlelo ezintsha zokuthuthukisa izikole ezisemiphakathini entulayo ngokuhlinzeka ngezinsiza ezanele kanye nokuthuthukisa ingqalasizinda. Lezi zinhlelo zibandakanya ukwakhiwa kwamagumbi okufundela amasha kanye nokulungiswa kwezakhiwo ezindala. Abafundi bazophinde bathole amathuba okuqeqeshwa okungeziwe emikhakheni ehlukahlukene ukuze bakwazi ukuthola amakhono asebenzayo. Abazali bakhuthazwa ukuba babambe iqhaza emisebenzini yesikole ukuze kuthuthukiswe imiphumela. Uhulumeni uthi lokhu kuyingxenye yomzamo wokunciphisa umehluko phakathi kwezikole ezisemadolobheni nezasemakhaya. Abaholi bezemfundo bakwamukele lokhu njengesinyathelo esibalulekile sokuthuthukisa izinga lemfundo ezweni."}
{"id": 5, "lang": "zu", "domain": "education", "text": "Abafundi abaningi ezikoleni eziphakeme ezweni lonke bazuze ohlelweni olusha lokufundisa olusebenzisa ubuchwepheshe besimanje ukuze kuthuthukiswe ukuqonda kwezifundo ezinzima. Uhulumeni uthi le ndlela ihlose ukwenza ukufunda kube lula futhi kube nentshisekelo enkulu kubafundi. Othisha bathole ukuqeqeshwa okusha ukuze bakwazi ukusebenzisa la mathuluzi ngendlela efanele ekilasini. Abafundi bakhuthazwa ukuthi basebenzise izinhlelo zokufunda ezengeziwe ukuze bathuthukise amakhono abo. Izikhulu zithi lokhu kuyingxenye yokulungiselela abafundi umnotho wesikhathi esizayo. Abazali bakubheke njengokuthuthukisa okuzokwenza izingane zabo zibe namathuba angcono emhlabeni wokusebenza."}
{"id": 6, "lang": "zu", "domain": "education", "text": "Eminyuziyamu yezemfundo nasezikhungweni zemfundo ephakeme kuqalwe uhlelo lokukhuthaza ucwaningo nokusungula izinto ezintsha phakathi kwabafundi nabacwaningi abasebasha. Uhulumeni uthi lolu hlelo luhlose ukukhulisa inani labantu abanamakhono ocwaningo ezweni. Abafundi bazothola ukwesekwa ngezimali kanye nokuqeqeshwa okujulile ukuze bakwazi ukwenza amaphrojekthi ocwaningo aphusile. Izikhungo zemfundo zithi lokhu kuzokhuthaza ukwakhiwa kwezixazululo zezinkinga zomphakathi. Abahlanganyeli bakhuthazwa ukuthi basebenzise leli thuba ukuze bathuthukise amakhono abo. Uhulumeni uthi lokhu kuyingxenye yokwakha isizwe esisekelwe olwazini nasekusunguleni."}
{"id": 7, "lang": "zu", "domain": "health", "text": "Emiphakathini eminingi yasemadolobheni kuqale umkhankaso omusha wokugoma abantu ukuze kuncishiswe ukusabalala kwezifo ezithathelwanayo. Uhulumeni uthi le nkqubo ihlose ukuvikela abantu abasengozini enkulu njengabantu abadala nezingane ezincane. Izikhungo zezempilo zisebenzisana nomphakathi ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuthi abantu bathola ulwazi olufanele mayelana nokubaluleka kokugoma. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuthi babambe iqhaza kulo mkhankaso ukuze bavikele imindeni yabo. Izisebenzi zezempilo zithi lokhu kuyingxenye yomzamo wokuthuthukisa impilo yomphakathi. Uhulumeni uthi uzosebenzisa izindlela zokwazisa ezahlukene ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuthi wonke umuntu uyafinyelelwa."}
{"id": 8, "lang": "zu", "domain": "health", "text": "Ekhuluma esibhedlela esikhulu saseThekwini, izikhulu zezempilo zichaze izinhlelo ezintsha zokunciphisa isikhathi sokulinda ezikhungweni zezempilo zomphakathi. Lolu hlelo luhlanganisa ukwandisa abasebenzi kanye nokuthuthukisa izinhlelo zokuhlela iziguli. Abantu abavakashela izikhungo zezempilo bakhuthazwa ukuthi basebenzise izinsiza zokuqala ezikhona ezindaweni zabo ukuze kuncishiswe ukugcwala ezibhedlela ezinkulu. Uhulumeni uthi lokhu kuyingxenye yokuthuthukisa ikhwalithi yezinsiza zezempilo ezweni. Abahlali bakwamukele lokhu kodwa bacele ukuthi kube nokuphuculwa okusheshayo ezindaweni ezisemakhaya lapho izinsiza zisancane kakhulu."}
{"id": 9, "lang": "zu", "domain": "health", "text": "Ngemuva kokwanda kwezifo ezihlobene nendlela yokuphila, uhulumeni umemezele uhlelo lokukhuthaza impilo enempilo ngokugxila ekudleni okunempilo nokuzivocavoca emiphakathini. Lolu hlelo luhlose ukunciphisa izifo ezifana nomfutho wegazi ophezulu nesifo sikashukela. Izisebenzi zezempilo zizovakashela imiphakathi ukuze zinikeze imfundo ngezindlela zokuphila ezilungile. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuthi babambe iqhaza emisebenzini yokuzivocavoca ehlelwa ezindaweni zomphakathi. Uhulumeni uthi lokhu kuyingxenye yomzamo wokuthuthukisa impilo yabantu ezweni lonke."}
{"id": 10, "lang": "zu", "domain": "infrastructure", "text": "Emadolobheni aseMpumalanga Kapa kuqale uhlelo olusha lokulungisa imigwaqo emikhulu eyonakele kakhulu ebangele ukulibaziseka kwezokuthutha. Umasipala uthi amaqembu okwakha asevele aqalile ukugcwalisa imigodi nokuvuselela izingxenye zomgwaqo ezindala. Abashayeli bakhuthazwa ukuba basebenzise eminye imigwaqo ngesikhathi sokulungiswa ukuze kugwenywe izingozi. Uhulumeni uthi uzosebenzisa izinhlelo zokubeka iso ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuthi umsebenzi wenziwa kahle. Abahlali bakubheke njengokuthuthukisa okuzothuthukisa ukuhamba kwansuku zonke kanye nomnotho wendawo."}
{"id": 11, "lang": "zu", "domain": "infrastructure", "text": "Ngaphezulu kwemiphakathi eminingi yasemakhaya kuqale uhlelo lokuthuthukisa ukuhlinzekwa kwamanzi ahlanzekile kanye nogesi ukuze kuthuthukiswe izinga lokuphila. Uhulumeni uthi le projekthi ihlose ukunciphisa ukushoda kwezinsiza eziyisisekelo ezindaweni ezikude. Izisebenzi zikamasipala sezivele zifaka amapayipi amasha kanye nokulungisa izinhlelo zikagesi ezindala. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuthi basebenzise izinsiza ngendlela esimeme ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukusimama kwesikhathi eside. Uhulumeni uthi lokhu kuyingxenye yomzamo wokwakha imiphakathi enokulingana nenempilo engcono."}
{"id": 1,"lang": "xh","domain":"government","text":"Ngaphezulu kweendawo ezisemaphandleni nakwiidolophu ezincinci kuqaliswe inkqubo entsha karhulumente yokuphucula ukufikelela kwiinkonzo zoluntu. Le nkqubo ijolise ekwandiseni izibonelelo ezisisiseko ezifana namanzi acocekileyo, umbane, kunye neendlela zokuhamba ezikhuselekileyo. Amagosa karhulumente athi umsebenzi uza kwenziwa ngokwezigaba ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuba zonke iindawo ziyafikelelwa ngaphandle kokulibaziseka okukhulu. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuba bathathe inxaxheba kwiintlanganiso zoluntu ukuze banike izimvo zabo malunga nezidingo eziphambili. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo iyinxalenye yesicwangciso esibanzi sokunciphisa ukungalingani phakathi kweendawo ezisemaphandleni nezisezidolophini. Uluntu luthi luyawamkela la manyathelo kodwa lucela ukuba kubekho ukubeka esweni okuqinileyo ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukusebenza kakuhle."}
{"id": 2,"lang":"xh","domain":"municipal_services","text":"Umasipala wesixeko saseBuffalo City ubhengeze isicwangciso esitsha sokulungisa imibhobho yamanzi emidala ebangela ukuphazamiseka okuphindaphindiweyo kunikezelo lwamanzi. Le projekthi iza kugxila kwiindawo ezichaphazeleke kakhulu kukuqhekeka kwemibhobho kunye nokuvuza kwamanzi. Amaqela ezobunjineli sele eqalile umsebenzi wokutshintsha iinxalenye ezonakeleyo ukuze kuphuculwe uzinzo lwenkqubo. Abahlali baceliwe ukuba basebenzise amanzi ngokonga ngexesha lokuqhutywa kwalo msebenzi. Umasipala uthi le nkqubo iza kunceda ukunciphisa ilahleko yamanzi nokuphucula ukusebenza kweenkonzo. Uluntu lukhuthazwe ukuba luhlale lunxibelelana namagosa ukuze kubikwe iingxaki ngokukhawuleza."}
{"id": 3,"lang":"xh","domain":"civic_affairs","text":"Ngexesha lentlanganiso kawonke-wonke eQonce abahlali bavakalise iinkxalabo zabo malunga nokulibaziseka kokuqokelelwa kwenkunkuma kunye nokukhanya kwezitalato okungasebenzi kakuhle. Amagosa kamasipala achaze ukuba kukho ukunqongophala kwezixhobo kunye nabasebenzi okuchaphazela ukuhanjiswa kweenkonzo. Urhulumente wasekhaya uthe sele kuqaliswe inkqubo yokongeza izixhobo ezitsha kunye nokuqesha abasebenzi abongezelelweyo. Abahlali baceliwe ukuba babe nomonde ngelixa kuqhubeka ukuphuculwa kweenkonzo. Iinkokeli zoluntu zithi kubalulekile ukomeleza unxibelelwano phakathi koluntu norhulumente ukuze iingxaki zisonjululwe ngokukhawuleza. Le ntlanganiso ithathwa njengenyathelo elibalulekileyo lokuphucula intsebenziswano."}
{"id": 4,"lang":"xh","domain":"government","text":"Urhulumente wesizwe ubhengeze inkqubo entsha yokwandisa amathuba engqesho kulutsha ngokusebenzisa iinkqubo zoqeqesho ezisekelwe kumashishini. Le nkqubo iza kudibanisa uqeqesho lwethiyori kunye namava asebenzayo emsebenzini ukuze kuphuculwe izakhono zabantu abatsha. Amashishini abucala aya kubambisana norhulumente ekuboneleleni ngamathuba oqeqesho kwiindawo ezahlukeneyo. Abantu abatsha bakhuthazwa ukuba babhalise kule nkqubo ukuze bakwazi ukufumana izakhono ezifunekayo kwimarike yomsebenzi. Urhulumente uthi le ndlela iza kunceda ukunciphisa izinga eliphezulu lokungaqeshwa. Uluntu luthi lulindele ukuba le nkqubo izise utshintsho olubonakalayo."}
{"id": 5,"lang":"xh","domain":"municipal_services","text":"Umasipala waseNelson Mandela Bay ubhengeze inkqubo yokuphucula izibane zezitalato kwiindawo ezichaphazelekayo ziziganeko zobugebenga ebusuku. Le nkqubo ijolise ekwandiseni ukhuseleko lwabahlali ngokufaka izibane ezonga amandla nezisebenza ixesha elide. Amaqela asebenzayo sele eqalile ukutshintsha izibane ezindala ezonakeleyo. Abahlali bavakalise ulonwabo ngeli nyathelo kodwa bacela ukuba umsebenzi ukhawuleziswe. Umasipala uthi le projekthi iya kuqhubeka de zonke iindawo eziphambili zifumane ukukhanya okwaneleyo. Urhulumente wasekhaya uthi ukhuseleko loluntu luyinto ephambili kule nkqubo."}
{"id": 6,"lang":"xh","domain":"civic_affairs","text":"Abahlali baseGqeberha babambe indibano yokuxoxa ngeengxaki zokuthuthwa kwezithuthi zikawonke-wonke kunye nokulibaziseka kweenkonzo zothutho. Amagosa ezothutho achaze ukuba kukho imingeni yokuguga kwezithuthi kunye nokunqongophala kwemali yokulungisa inkqubo. Urhulumente uthe sele eqalile inkqubo yokuvuselela izithuthi kunye nokuphucula iindlela zothutho. Abahlali baceliwe ukuba basebenzisane namagosa ngokunika ingxelo rhoqo. Le nkqubo ijolise ekuphuculeni ukuhamba kwabantu mihla le. Iinkokeli zoluntu zithi intsebenziswano iyimfuneko ukuze kufezekiswe iziphumo ezilungileyo."}
{"id": 7,"lang":"xh","domain":"government","text":"Ngaphezulu kwezikolo ezininzi ezisemaphandleni kuqaliswe inkqubo entsha yokuphucula izibonelelo zemfundo ngokuhambisa izixhobo zokufunda kunye noqeqesho lootitshala. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo ijolise ekuphuculeni iziphumo zabafundi kwizifundo ezibalulekileyo ezifana nezibalo nesayensi. Ootitshala bafumana uqeqesho olongezelelweyo ukuze bakwazi ukusebenzisa iindlela ezintsha zokufundisa. Abafundi bakhuthazwa ukuba basebenzise amathuba okufunda angezelelweyo ukuze baphucule iziphumo zabo. Uluntu luthi luyayixhasa le nkqubo kodwa lucela ukuba kubekho ukubeka esweni ukuqinisekisa impumelelo. Urhulumente uthi le projekthi iyinxalenye yesicwangciso semfundo eside."}
{"id": 8,"lang":"xh","domain":"municipal_services","text":"Umasipala waseThekwini ubhengeze inkqubo yokuphucula ukuqokelelwa kwenkunkuma emva kokwanda kwezikhalazo zabahlali kwiindawo ezahlukeneyo. Le nkqubo iza kusebenzisa iishedyuli ezintsha kunye nezithuthi ezongeziweyo ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukucoceka kweendawo zokuhlala. Amagosa athi oku kuya kunciphisa ingozi yezifo ezibangelwa yinkunkuma eqokelelekileyo. Abahlali baceliwe ukuba balandele imihla ebekiweyo yokukhupha inkunkuma. Urhulumente wasekhaya uthi le nkqubo iza kuqhubeka ngokubeka iliso rhoqo. Uluntu lukhuthazwe ukuba lusebenzisane ukuze kugcinwe ucoceko."}
{"id": 9,"lang":"xh","domain":"civic_affairs","text":"Ngexesha lengxoxo yoluntu eMthatha abahlali bavakalise inkxalabo malunga nokungalingani ekufikeleleni kwiinkonzo zamanzi nezempilo. Amagosa karhulumente athe achaza izicwangciso zokwandisa izibonelelo kwezi ndawo ukuze kuncitshiswe le ngxaki. Urhulumente uthi sele kuqaliswe iiprojekthi ezintsha zokuphucula uthungelwano lwamanzi kunye nokwandisa iikliniki. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuba bathathe inxaxheba kwiinkqubo zophuhliso ukuze kuvakaliswe iimfuno zabo. Iinkokeli zoluntu zithi kubalulekile ukuqinisekisa ukuba akukho mmandla ushiywayo ngaphandle kweenkonzo ezibalulekileyo."}
{"id": 10,"lang":"xh","domain":"government","text":"Urhulumente wesifundazwe ubhengeze inkqubo yokuphucula ulawulo lweenkonzo zoluntu ngokusebenzisa iinkqubo zedijithali zokulandelela izikhalazo zabahlali. Le nkqubo ijolise ekunciphiseni ukulibaziseka nasekuphuculeni ukuphendula kumaxesha akhawulezayo. Amagosa athi abantu baza kukwazi ukulandelela imeko yezikhalazo zabo ngexesha lokwenyani. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuba basebenzise ezi nkqubo ukuze kube lula ukulungisa iingxaki. Urhulumente uthi le ndlela iza kwandisa ukungafihli kunye noxanduva kulawulo lwezibonelelo zoluntu."}
{"id": 1,"lang":"xh","domain":"government","text":"Ngaphezulu kweendawo ezininzi ezisemaphandleni eMpuma Koloni kuqaliswe inkqubo entsha karhulumente yokuphucula ukufikelela kwiinkonzo ezisisiseko. Le nkqubo ijolise ekwandiseni amanzi acocekileyo, umbane, kunye nokuphucula iindlela ezidibanisa iilali nezixeko. Amagosa karhulumente athi umsebenzi uza kwenziwa ngezigaba ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuba akukho lali ishiywa ngaphandle kophuhliso. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuba bathathe inxaxheba kwiintlanganiso zophuhliso ukuze banike izimvo zabo. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo iyinxalenye yesicwangciso sokunciphisa ukungalingani kwezentlalo phakathi kweendawo ezahlukeneyo. Uluntu luthi lulindele ukuphucuka okubonakalayo kwiinyanga ezizayo."}
