{"id": 1,"lang":"xh","domain":"government","text":"Ngaphezulu kweendawo ezahlukeneyo ezisemaphandleni nakwiidolophu ezincinci kuqaliswe inkqubo entsha karhulumente ejolise ekuphuculeni ukuhanjiswa kweenkonzo zoluntu. Le nkqubo igxile ekwandiseni ukufikelela kumanzi acocekileyo, umbane ozinzileyo, kunye neendlela ezikhuselekileyo ezidibanisa uluntu. Amagosa karhulumente athi umsebenzi uza kwenziwa ngokwezigaba ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuba zonke iindawo zifumana ingqwalasela efanelekileyo. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuba bathathe inxaxheba kwiintlanganiso zophuhliso ukuze banike izimvo zabo ngeemfuno eziphambili. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo iyinxalenye yesicwangciso esibanzi sokunciphisa ukungalingani phakathi kweendawo ezisemaphandleni nezisezidolophini. Uluntu luthi lulindele ukuphucuka okubonakalayo kwiinyanga ezizayo njengoko iiprojekthi ziqhubeka nokuphunyezwa ngokuthe ngcembe."}
{"id": 2,"lang":"xh","domain":"social_grants","text":"Ngaphezulu kweentsapho ezizinkulungwane ezininzi ezweni lonke ziyaqhubeka nokuxhamla kwizibonelelo zikarhulumente ezijolise ekuncedeni abantu abahlwempuzekileyo nabasengozini. Le nkqubo yezibonelelo ijolise ekunciphiseni indlala nokunceda abantu abadala, abantwana, nabantu abakhubazekileyo ukuba bakwazi ukuhlangabezana neemfuno zabo zemihla ngemihla. Amagosa karhulumente athi iinkqubo zokuhlawula ziphuculwe ukuze kuncitshiswe ukulibaziseka nokwandisa ukufikelela kwabahlomulayo. Abahlomulayo bakhuthazwa ukuba basebenzise iindlela ezisemthethweni zokubhalisa ukuze kuphetshwe ukukhwabanisa. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo iyinxalenye yomzamo wokwakha uluntu olulinganayo noluzinzileyo apho kungabikho mntu ushiywa ngaphandle kwenkxaso eyimfuneko. Iinkokeli zoluntu zithi kubalulekile ukubeka iliso ukuqinisekisa ukuba uncedo lufikelela kubantu abahlosiweyo kuphela."}
{"id": 3,"lang":"xh","domain":"housing_support","text":"Emva kokukhula kwemfuno yezindlu ezikhuselekileyo nezifikelelekayo, urhulumente ubhengeze uhlelo olutsha lokwakhiwa kwezindlu kumaphondo ahlukeneyo. Le nkqubo ijolise ekuncedeni imindeni ehlala kwiindawo ezingekho mthethweni okanye ezisemngciphekweni wezikhukhula. Izindlu ezakhiwayo ziya kubonelelwa ngamanzi acocekileyo, umbane, kunye nenkqubo yogutyulo eyaneleyo. Amagosa athi uluhlu lwabahlomulayo luza kulawulwa ngokusesikweni ukuze kuqinisekiswe ubulungisa. Abahlali baceliwe ukuba babhalise kwiiofisi zikamasipala ukuze bakwazi ukufakwa kuluhlu. Urhulumente uthi le projekthi ijolise ekuphuculeni izinga lokuphila kunye nokwakha imiphakathi ekhuselekileyo nenokuzinza ixesha elide."}
{"id": 4,"lang":"xh","domain":"community_welfare","text":"Ngaphakathi kwemiphakathi emininzi ezidolophini kuqaliswe inkqubo yokuxhasa iintsapho ezijongene nobunzima bezemali nokungaqeshwa. Le nkqubo ibandakanya ukuhanjiswa kokutya, iingcebiso zengqesho, kunye noqeqesho lwezakhono ukuze abantu bakwazi ukuzimela. Amagosa eenkonzo zentlalo asebenzisana nemibutho yasekuhlaleni ukwandisa ukufikelela kolu ncedo. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuba bathathe inxaxheba kwiinkqubo zokuqeqeshwa ukuze baphucule amathuba abo emisebenzi. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo iyinxalenye yesicwangciso sokunciphisa indlala nokwakha uluntu olunamandla. Iinkokeli zoluntu zithi olu ncedo lubalulekile ngakumbi kumakhaya angenayo ingeniso ezinzileyo."}
{"id": 5,"lang":"xh","domain":"social_grants","text":"Urhulumente wesizwe ubhengeze ukuba izibonelelo zabantu abadala ziya kuhlaziywa ukuze zihambelane nokunyuka kweendleko zokuphila. Le nkqubo ijolise ekuncedeni abantu abadala ukuba bakwazi ukuhlangabezana neemfuno ezifana nokutya, amayeza, kunye neendleko zezindlu. Amagosa athi iintlawulo ziya kuqhubeka ngendlela eqhelekileyo kodwa ziphuculwe ngokweendlela zokuhlawula zedijithali. Abahlomulayo baceliwe ukuba baqinisekise ukuba iinkcukacha zabo zihlaziywa rhoqo ukuze kungabikho ziphazamiso. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo ibonisa ukuzibophelela ekukhathaleleni abantu abasengozini. Uluntu luthi olu tshintsho luzisa ithemba ngakumbi kumakhaya amaninzi axhomekeke kwezi zibonelelo."}
{"id": 6,"lang":"xh","domain":"housing_support","text":"Ngaphezulu kwemimandla yaseGoli kuqaliswe inkqubo yokuphucula izindlu ezindala nokulungisa iindawo zokuhlala ezingahlangabezani nemigangatho yokhuseleko. Le nkqubo ijolise ekunciphiseni umngcipheko wezikhukhula kunye nokudilika kwezakhiwo ezindala. Amagosa kamasipala athi iintsapho ezichaphazelekayo ziya kufuduselwa kwizindlu ezikhuselekileyo ngexesha lomsebenzi. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuba basebenzisane nabasebenzi ukuze kuqhutywe umsebenzi ngokukhawuleza nangokukhuselekileyo. Urhulumente uthi le projekthi ijolise ekwakheni iindawo zokuhlala ezizinzileyo nezihambelana neemfuno zabantu. Iinkokeli zoluntu zithi le nkqubo iza kuzisa ukuphucuka okukhulu kumgangatho wobomi."}
{"id": 7,"lang":"xh","domain":"community_welfare","text":"Emva kokunyuka kweengxaki zokungabikho kwemisebenzi kulutsha, urhulumente ubhengeze inkqubo yokuxhasa abantu abatsha ngemisebenzi yesikhashana kunye noqeqesho lwamakhono. Le nkqubo ijolise ekunciphiseni indlala nokwandisa amathuba engqesho kumacandelo ahlukeneyo. Amashishini abucala nawo aya kubandakanywa ekuboneleleni ngamathuba oqeqesho. Abantu abatsha bakhuthazwa ukuba basebenzise eli thuba ukuze bakhe ikamva elizinzileyo. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo iyinxalenye yesicwangciso sokwakha uqoqosho olubandakanya wonke umntu. Uluntu luthi olu ncedo lubalulekile ekuphuculeni amathuba abantu abatsha."}
{"id": 8,"lang":"xh","domain":"social_grants","text":"Ngaphezulu kweentsapho ezisemaphandleni ziyaqhubeka nokuxhamla kwizibonelelo zokutya kunye nenkxaso yemali enikezelwa ngurhulumente. Le nkqubo ijolise ekuncedeni imiphakathi echaphazelekayo yintlupheko kunye nokungabikho kwemisebenzi. Amagosa athi ukuhanjiswa koncedo kuyenziwa ngokucwangcisiweyo ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuba akukho mntu ushiywayo ngaphandle. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuba babike naziphi na iingxaki zokufikelela kuncedo. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo yinxalenye yomzamo wokunciphisa indlala nokuphucula impilo yoluntu. Iinkokeli zoluntu zithi olu ncedo lubalulekile ngakumbi kwiindawo ezikude."}
{"id": 9,"lang":"xh","domain":"housing_support","text":"Umasipala waseThekwini ubhengeze inkqubo yokwakha izindlu ezintsha kubantu abahlala kwiindawo ezingekho mthethweni ezisemngciphekweni wezikhukhula. Le projekthi ijolise ekuboneleleni ngeendawo zokuhlala ezikhuselekileyo nezisemthethweni. Amagosa athi uluhlu lwabahlomulayo luza kulawulwa ngokungqongqo ukuze kuqinisekiswe ubulungisa. Abahlali baceliwe ukuba basebenzisane ngexesha lokufuduswa ukuze kugwenywe ukungqubana. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo iza kuphucula izinga lokuphila kwaye inciphise umngcipheko weentlekele zemvelo. Iinkokeli zoluntu zithi kubalulekile ukuba inkqubo iqhutywe ngokungafihli."}
{"id": 10,"lang":"xh","domain":"community_welfare","text":"Ngaphakathi kwemiphakathi yasemadolophini kuqaliswe inkqubo yokuxhasa abantu abangenayo ingeniso ezinzileyo ngokubanika ukutya, iingcebiso, kunye noqeqesho lwamakhono. Le nkqubo ijolise ekunciphiseni indlala nokwandisa ukuzimela kwabahlali. Amagosa eenkonzo zentlalo asebenzisana nemibutho yasekuhlaleni ukwandisa ukufikelela kolu ncedo. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuba bathathe inxaxheba kwiinkqubo zokuqeqeshwa ukuze baphucule amathuba abo. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo iyinxalenye yomzamo wokwakha uluntu oluzinzileyo nolunamathuba alinganayo. Iinkokeli zoluntu zithi olu ncedo luzisa ithemba kumakhaya amaninzi."}
{"id": 11,"lang":"xh","domain":"social_grants","text":"Urhulumente ubhengeze inkqubo entsha yokuphucula ukuhanjiswa kwezibonelelo kubantu abakhubazekileyo ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuba bafumana uncedo ngokukhawuleza nangokufanelekileyo. Le nkqubo ijolise ekunciphiseni ukubambezeleka kunye nokwandisa ukufikelela kwiinkonzo ezibalulekileyo. Amagosa athi iinkqubo zedijithali ziya kusetyenziswa ukulandelela iintlawulo kunye nokunciphisa ubuqhophololo. Abahlomulayo bakhuthazwa ukuba baqinisekise ukuba iinkcukacha zabo zihlaziywa rhoqo. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo ibonisa ukuzibophelela ekuxhaseni abantu abasengozini. Uluntu luthi olu tshintsho luzisa ithemba kunye nokhuseleko olungcono kubahlali abaxhomekeke kolu ncedo."}
{"id": 12,"lang":"xh","domain":"community_welfare","text":"Emva kokunyuka kweengxaki zentlupheko kwezinye iindawo, urhulumente ubhengeze inkqubo yokwakha amaziko oncedo olungxamisekileyo aya kubonelela ngokutya, indawo yokuhlala, kunye neengcebiso kubantu abasengxakini. La maziko aya kusebenzisana nemibutho yasekuhlaleni ukuqinisekisa ukuba uncedo lufikelela ngokukhawuleza. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuba basebenzise ezi nkonzo xa besengxakini. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo ijolise ekunciphiseni indlala nokukhusela abantu abasengozini enkulu. Iinkokeli zoluntu zithi la manyathelo abalulekile ekwakheni uluntu olunenkathalo noluxhasanayo."}
{"id": 1,"lang":"xh","domain":"agriculture","text":"Ngaphezulu kweefama ezisemaphandleni aseMpuma Koloni kuqaliswe inkqubo entsha karhulumente yokuxhasa abalimi abancinci ngokubonelela ngembewu ephuculiweyo nezichumiso. Le nkqubo ijolise ekwandiseni imveliso yokutya kunye nokunciphisa indlala kwiindawo ezisemngciphekweni wokungabikho kokutya. Amagosa ezolimo athi abalimi baza kufumana uqeqesho olongezelelweyo malunga neendlela zokulima ezimelana nokutshintsha kwemozulu. Abahlali basemaphandleni bakhuthazwa ukuba babhalise ukuze bafumane le nkxaso. Urhulumente uthi le projekthi iyinxalenye yesicwangciso esibanzi sokuphuhlisa ezolimo ezizinzileyo. Iinkokeli zoluntu zithi olu ncedo luzisa ithemba elitsha kumakhaya axhomekeke kwezolimo."}
{"id": 2,"lang":"xh","domain":"rural_development","text":"Emaphandleni aseLimpopo kuqaliswe inkqubo yokuphucula iindlela zokufikelela ezimakethe ukuze abalimi bakwazi ukuthengisa iimveliso zabo ngokulula. Le nkqubo ijolise ekwakheni iindlela ezintsha kunye nokulungisa ezonakeleyo ezixhumanisa iilali nezixeko ezikufutshane. Amagosa karhulumente athi oku kuza kunciphisa iindleko zokuthutha kwaye kunyuse ingeniso yamakhaya asemaphandleni. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuba bathathe inxaxheba kwiingxoxo zophuhliso ukuze bachaze iimfuno zabo. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo iyinxalenye yesicwangciso sokuphuhlisa uqoqosho lwasezilalini. Iinkokeli zoluntu zithi le projekthi iza kuzisa utshintsho olubonakalayo kubomi babahlali."}
{"id": 3,"lang":"xh","domain":"agriculture","text":"Ngexesha lonyaka omtsha wokulima, urhulumente ubhengeze inkxaso eyongezelelweyo kubalimi bombona kunye nengqolowa ukuze konyuswe ukhuseleko lokutya. Le nkxaso ibandakanya izibonelelo zemali, izixhobo zokulima, kunye noqeqesho kwiindlela zokulima ezisebenzayo. Amagosa athi injongo kukunciphisa ukuxhomekeka ekuthengisweni kokutya kumazwe angaphandle. Abalimi bakhuthazwa ukuba basebenzise iindlela ezonga amanzi ukuze bakwazi ukumelana nemozulu eyomileyo. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo iza kunceda ukwakha ukhuseleko lokutya oluzinzileyo. Iinkokeli zezolimo zithi le nkxaso ibalulekile ekuphuculeni imveliso yezolimo."}
{"id": 4,"lang":"xh","domain":"rural_development","text":"Ngaphezulu kweelali ezikude ezisemaphandleni aseKwaZulu-Natali kuqaliswe inkqubo yokufaka amanzi acocekileyo kunye nokulungisa imithombo yakudala. Le nkqubo ijolise ekunciphiseni ubunzima bokufikelela emanzini kubahlali abasemaphandleni. Amagosa kamasipala athi iipayipi ezintsha sele zifakwa kwezinye iindawo ezichaphazelekayo. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuba basebenzise amanzi ngendlela enoxanduva ukuze kugcinwe uzinzo. Urhulumente uthi le projekthi iyinxalenye yesicwangciso sokuphucula iziseko ezingundoqo. Iinkokeli zoluntu zithi le nkqubo iza kuphucula kakhulu umgangatho wobomi."}
{"id": 5,"lang":"xh","domain":"agriculture","text":"Abalimi abancinci kwiindawo ezahlukeneyo zelizwe bafumene inkxaso entsha yokugcina izilwanyana kunye nokuphucula imveliso yobisi. Le nkqubo ibandakanya uqeqesho lweendlela zokukhathalela izilwanyana kunye nokuthintela izifo ezifumaneka kwiifama. Amagosa ezolimo athi oku kuza kunceda ukwandisa ingeniso yamakhaya asemaphandleni. Abalimi bakhuthazwa ukuba basebenzise iinkonzo zikarhulumente ukuze bafumane uncedo olufanelekileyo. Urhulumente uthi le projekthi ijolise ekwakheni uqoqosho lwezolimo oluzinzileyo. Iinkokeli zoluntu zithi le nkxaso iza kuphucula uzinzo lokutya kwiindawo ezininzi."}
{"id": 6,"lang":"xh","domain":"education","text":"Ngaphezulu kwezikolo ezisemaphandleni kuqaliswe inkqubo yokuphucula izibonelelo zemfundo ngokubonelela ngezixhobo zokufunda kunye noqeqesho lootitshala. Le nkqubo ijolise ekuphuculeni iziphumo zabafundi kwizifundo ezibalulekileyo ezifana nezibalo nesayensi. Ootitshala bafumana uqeqesho olongezelelweyo ukuze bakwazi ukusebenzisa iindlela ezintsha zokufundisa. Abafundi bakhuthazwa ukuba bathathe inxaxheba kwizifundo ezongezelelweyo ukuze baphucule iziphumo zabo. Urhulumente uthi le projekthi iyinxalenye yesicwangciso semfundo eside. Iinkokeli zemfundo zithi olu phuculo luza kuzisa utshintsho oluhle kwizikolo zasemaphandleni."}
{"id": 7,"lang":"xh","domain":"education","text":"Emva kokukhula kwenkxalabo malunga nokuphumelela kwabafundi, urhulumente ubhengeze inkqubo yokuxhasa abafundi kwiiyunivesithi ngokunyusa izibonelelo zokufunda. Le nkqubo ijolise ekunciphiseni ukulahlwa kwabafundi ngenxa yeengxaki zemali. Iiyunivesithi zithi ziza kusebenzisana norhulumente ukuqinisekisa ukuba inkxaso ifikelela kubafundi abafanelekileyo. Abafundi bakhuthazwa ukuba basebenzise iinkonzo zokuxhasa ezifumanekayo ezikhampasini. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo iza kunceda ukwakha isizukulwana esinamakhono aphezulu. Iinkokeli zemfundo zithi le nkxaso ibalulekile ekuphuhliseni uqoqosho lwexesha elizayo."}
{"id": 8,"lang":"xh","domain":"education","text":"Ngaphezulu kwezikolo eziphakamileyo kuqaliswe inkqubo yokuphucula ukufunda kwezibalo nesayensi ngokusebenzisa ubuchwepheshe bale mihla. Le nkqubo ibandakanya iikhompyutha ezintsha kunye nezixhobo zokufunda zedijithali. Ootitshala bafumana uqeqesho lokusebenzisa obu buchwepheshe ekufundiseni. Abafundi bakhuthazwa ukuba basebenzise izixhobo zedijithali ukuphucula ukuqonda kwezifundo. Urhulumente uthi le projekthi ijolise ekulungiseleleni abafundi imisebenzi yexesha elizayo. Iinkokeli zemfundo zithi oku kuza kuphucula iziphumo zabafundi ngokubanzi."}
{"id": 9,"lang":"xh","domain":"education","text":"Emva kweengxoxo zikazwelonke ngemfundo, urhulumente ubhengeze izicwangciso zokwakha izikolo ezintsha kwiindawo ezinemfuno ephezulu. Le nkqubo ijolise ekunciphiseni ukuxinana kwabafundi nokuphucula umgangatho wokufunda. Izikolo ezindala nazo ziza kulungiswa ukuze zihambelane nemigangatho yokhuseleko. Abazali bakhuthazwa ukuba bathathe inxaxheba kwiikomiti zesikolo ukuze kuphuculwe ulawulo. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo iyinxalenye yesicwangciso semfundo esibanzi. Iinkokeli zoluntu zithi olu phuhliso luza kuba nefuthe elihle kwizizukulwana ezizayo."}
{"id": 10,"lang":"xh","domain":"education","text":"Ngaphezulu kwezikolo ezisemaphandleni kuqaliswe inkqubo yokuxhasa abafundi ngokutya kwesikolo kunye nezixhobo zokufunda ezisisiseko. Le nkqubo ijolise ekuphuculeni ukuzimasa kwabafundi nasekunciphiseni ukulahlwa kwezikolo. Ootitshala bathi oku kunceda abafundi ukuba bagxile ngakumbi kwizifundo zabo. Abazali bakhuthazwa ukuba basebenzisane nezikolo ukuze kuqinisekiswe impumelelo yabafundi. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo iyinxalenye yesicwangciso sokuphucula imfundo esisiseko. Iinkokeli zemfundo zithi le nkxaso iza kunceda ukwakha ikamva eliqinileyo labafundi."}
{"id": 11,"lang":"xh","domain":"education","text":"Ngaphakathi kweeyunivesithi ezahlukeneyo kuqaliswe inkqubo yokukhuthaza uphando kunye nophuhliso lwezakhono ezintsha phakathi kwabafundi nabaphandi. Le nkqubo ijolise ekwandiseni inani lophando olusombulula iingxaki zoluntu. Abafundi bafumana inkxaso yemali kunye noqeqesho ukuze bakwazi ukwenza iiprojekthi zophando ezisemgangathweni ophezulu. Iiyunivesithi zithi le nkqubo iza kunceda ukwakha uqoqosho olusekwe kulwazi. Abafundi bakhuthazwa ukuba basebenzise eli thuba ukuphuhlisa amakhono abo. Urhulumente uthi le projekthi iyinxalenye yesicwangciso sokwakha isizwe esisekelwe kwisayensi nolwazi."}
{"id": 1,"lang":"xh","domain":"health","text":"Emaphandleni nakwiidolophu ezincinci kuqaliswe umkhankaso omtsha wezempilo ojolise ekwandiseni ulwazi malunga nezifo ezosulelayo kunye nokubaluleka kokuhlolwa kwempilo rhoqo. Amagosa ezempilo athi le nkqubo iza kubandakanya ukuhanjiswa kolwazi ezikolweni, kwiikliniki, nakwiintlanganiso zoluntu ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuba abantu bafikelelwa lulwazi oluchanekileyo. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuba basebenzise iinkonzo zeekliniki zikamasipala ukuze bahlolwe kwangexesha. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo iyinxalenye yesicwangciso sokuphucula impilo yoluntu nokunciphisa ukufa okunokuthintelwa. Iingcali zempilo zithi ukufundisa uluntu kudlala indima ebalulekileyo ekuthinteleni ukusasazeka kwezifo. Uluntu luthi luyalwamkela olu phulo kwaye lulindele ukuphucuka kwempilo kwiindawo zalo."}
{"id": 2,"lang":"xh","domain":"health","text":"Izibhedlele zikawonke-wonke ezikumaphondo ahlukeneyo ziye zaqalisa inkqubo yokunciphisa ixesha lokulinda kwizigulane ngokwandisa abasebenzi kunye nokuphucula inkqubo yokwamkelwa. Amagosa ezempilo athi le nkqubo ijolise ekuphuculeni umgangatho weenkonzo kunye nokunciphisa ukuxinana kwizibhedlele ezinkulu. Iikliniki ezikufutshane nazo zikhuthazwa ukuba ziphathe iimeko ezingxamisekileyo ezincinci ukuze kuncitshiswe uxinzelelo kwizibhedlele. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuba basebenzise iinkonzo zokuqala phambi kokuba baye kwizibhedlele ezikhulu. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo iya kuphucula ukusebenza kwenkqubo yezempilo ngokubanzi. Iinkokeli zoluntu zithi olu tshintsho liza kunceda kakhulu abantu abasengozini."}
{"id": 3,"lang":"xh","domain":"health","text":"Ngaphezulu kweendawo ezininzi ezisemaphandleni kuqaliswe inkqubo yokugonya abantu ukuze kuncitshiswe ukusasazeka kwezifo ezithathelwanayo. Amagosa ezempilo athi le nkqubo ijolise ekukhuseleni abantu abadala, abantwana, kunye nabantu abaneemeko zempilo ezibuthathaka. Iindawo zokugonya ziye zasasazwa kwiikliniki nakwiindawo zoluntu ukuze kufikelelwe abantu abaninzi. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuba bathathe inxaxheba ukuze bakhusele iintsapho zabo. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo iyinxalenye yomzamo wokuphucula ukhuseleko lwempilo yesizwe. Iingcali zithi ugonyo luyindlela ebalulekileyo yokuthintela izifo."}
{"id": 4,"lang":"xh","domain":"infrastructure","text":"Ngaphezulu kweendlela eziphambili ezidibanisa izixeko ezinkulu kuqaliswe inkqubo yokulungisa iindlela ezonakeleyo ezibangela iingozi rhoqo. Umasipala uthi amaqela okwakha sele eqalile ukugcwalisa imingxunya kunye nokuphucula umgangatho weendlela. Le nkqubo ijolise ekwandiseni ukhuseleko lwabashayeli nabahambi ngeenyawo. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuba balandele imiqondiso yokwakha ngexesha lomsebenzi. Urhulumente uthi le projekthi iza kunciphisa ukulibaziseka kwezithuthi kunye neengozi ezindleleni. Iinkokeli zoluntu zithi olu phuculo luyimfuneko ekuphuhliseni uqoqosho lwengingqi."}
{"id": 5,"lang":"xh","domain":"infrastructure","text":"Emaphandleni aseMpuma Koloni kuqaliswe inkqubo yokuphucula unikezelo lwamanzi acocekileyo ngokufaka iipayipi ezintsha kunye nokulungisa imithombo endala. Le nkqubo ijolise ekunciphiseni ukushoda kwamanzi okuhlala kuchaphazela imiphakathi ngexesha lasehlotyeni. Amagosa kamasipala athi umsebenzi uza kwenziwa ngezigaba ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukufikelela ngokulinganayo. Abahlali bakhuthazwa ukuba basebenzise amanzi ngokonga. Urhulumente uthi le projekthi iyinxalenye yesicwangciso sokuphucula iziseko ezingundoqo. Iinkokeli zoluntu zithi le nkqubo iza kuphucula kakhulu umgangatho wobomi."}
{"id": 6,"lang":"xh","domain":"community","text":"Emva kweminyaka yokulinda, abahlali baseQonce bagqibe ekubeni babhiyozele ukuvulwa kweholo entsha yoluntu esiza kusetyenziswa kwiintlanganiso, imicimbi yolutsha, kunye nemisebenzi yenkcubeko. Le holo yakhiwe njengenxalenye yenkqubo karhulumente yokuphuhlisa iindawo zoluntu. Amagosa athi le ndawo iza kunceda ekomelezeni ubudlelwane phakathi kwabahlali. Abahlali bavakalise uvuyo ngokuba ngoku banendawo efanelekileyo yokuhlangana. Urhulumente uthi le projekthi ijolise ekwakheni uluntu olunxibeleleneyo nolusebenzisanayo. Iinkokeli zoluntu zithi le holo iza kudlala indima ebalulekileyo ekuphuhliseni ulutsha."}
{"id": 7,"lang":"xh","domain":"culture","text":"Ngexesha lomnyhadala wenkcubeko waseMpuma Koloni, abahlali abavela kwiindawo ezahlukeneyo babonise umculo, umdaniso, kunye nobugcisa bemveli. Lo mnyhadala ujolise ekugcineni nasekukhuthazeni inkcubeko yabantu bommandla. Amagosa karhulumente athi imisitho efana nale inceda ekukhuthazeni ukhenketho lwengingqi kunye nokwakha uqoqosho lwasekuhlaleni. Abathathi-nxaxheba bavakalise ulonwabo ngokukwazi ukwabelana ngamasiko abo. Urhulumente uthi le nkqubo iyinxalenye yokuxhasa imvelaphi yenkcubeko yesizwe. Iinkokeli zoluntu zithi inkcubeko idlala indima ebalulekileyo ekwakheni ubunye phakathi kwabantu."}
{"id": 1, "lang": "ss", "domain": "government", "text": "Ngaphezulu kwemiphakatsi lehlukene eveni lonkhe, uhulumeni umemetele luhlelo lolusha loluhlose kuchubekisela embili kufinyelela kwetinsita temmango. Lolu hlelo lugcile ekukhuliseni emanti ahlobile, kugucula tinkinga temandla kagesi, kanye nekulungisa imigwaco lebalulekile. Tikhulu temmango titsi lomsebenti utawentiwa ngezigaba kuze kuqinisekiswe kutsi tonkhe tindzawo tiyafinyelelwa ngaphandle kwekubambezeleka lokukhulu. Bantfu bakhutsatwa kutsi babambe lichaza emihlanganweni yemphakatsi kuze banike imicabango yabo ngekutsi yikuphi lokubaluleke kakhulu. Uhulumeni utsi lolu hlelo luyincenye yesu lelikhulu lekunciphisa kungalingani emkhatsini wemadolobha netindzawo tasemaphandleni. Bantfu bemmango batsi balindzele kubona lushintjo lolubonakalako emnyakeni lotako njengoba emaphrojekthi achubeka asebenta ngekucophelela."}
{"id": 2, "lang": "ss", "domain": "municipal_services", "text": "Umasipala wedolobha lelikhulu umemetele luhlelo lolusha lwekulungisa imigwaco leyonakele leyibangela tingozi letinyenti emalanga onkhe. Lomsebenti ugcile etigwacweni letisetjentiswa kakhulu bantfu labahamba ngema-vehikeli kanye nalabahamba ngetinyawo. Tikhulu temasipala titsi emacembu ekwakha asebenta ngekushesha kugcwalisa imigodzi kanye nekulungisa tindzawo letigugile. Bantfu bakhutsatwa kutsi basebentise tindlela letinye uma imigwaco itsiwa isalungiswa kuze kugwenywe kuphatseka kabi kwetimoto. Uhulumeni wasekhaya utsi lolu hlelo lutawunciphisa tingozi futsi lukhuphule kuphepha emigwacweni. Emiphakatsi yemukele lolu hlelo kepha yacela kutsi umsebenzi usheshiswe kuze kuphila kwansuku tonkhe kungaphazamiseki kakhulu."}
{"id": 3, "lang": "ss", "domain": "civic_affairs", "text": "Emhlanganweni wemphakatsi lobewubanjelwe edolobheni, bantfu bavakalise tinkinga tabo mayelana nekubambezeleka kwetinsita letifana nekulandvwa kwedoti kanye nekukhanya kwemigwaco lokungasebenti kahle. Tikhulu temasipala tichazile kutsi kukhona kushoda kwetinsita kanye nesabelomali lesilinganiselwe lokuchaphata kushesha kwemsebenti. Uhulumeni wasekhaya utsi sewucale luhlelo lwekukhulisa tisetjentiswa kanye nekutfola basebenti labanye kuze kuncishiswe tinkinga. Bantfu bakhutsatwa kutsi babike tinkinga masinyane kuze kube lula kulungisa. Emholi wemphakatsi utsi kubambisana kubalulekile ekuphuculeni tinsita. Lomhlangano ubukwa njengendlela yekucinisa budlelwano emkhatsini wemphakatsi nohulumeni."}
{"id": 4, "lang": "ss", "domain": "government", "text": "Uhulumeni welive umemetele luhlelo lolusha lwekukhulisa ematfuba emsebenti kulusha ngekugxila ekuqeqesheni emakhono lasetjentiswako. Lolu hlelo lutawuhlanganisa kufundza ekilasini kanye nekusebenta etimbonini kuze bantfu labasha batfole lwati loluphelele. Emabhizinisi labucala atawubambisana nohulumeni ekunikeni ematfuba ekuqeqesha. Lusha lukhutsatwa kutsi lubhalise kuze lutfole emakhono ladzingekako emakethe yemsebenti. Uhulumeni utsi lolu hlelo lutawunciphisa liphasi lelikhulu lekungasebenti. Emiphakatsi itsi ilindzele kubona lushintjo loluhle ekusaseni lebantfu labasha."}
{"id": 5, "lang": "ss", "domain": "municipal_services", "text": "Umasipala waseThekwini umemetele luhlelo lwekuphucula kuhambisa emanti etindzaweni letivame kuba nenkinga yekuntuleka kwemanti. Lolu hlelo lugcile ekwakheni ematanki lamasha kanye nekulungisa emapayipi lamadzala. Tikhulu titsi sekucalile kuhlolwa tindzawo letisengotini lephakeme kuze kubekwe kuhle kusebenta. Bantfu bakhutsatwa kutsi basebentise emanti ngekuwonga kuze kugcinwe kusimama kwalomsebenti. Uhulumeni wasekhaya utsi utawusebentisa tindlela tekwazisa umphakatsi kuze bantfu bati kahle ngalokubalulekile. Lomsebenti ulindzeleke kutsi unciphise kakhulu tinkinga temanti esifundzeni."}
{"id": 6, "lang": "ss", "domain": "civic_affairs", "text": "Bantfu baseNelson Mandela Bay babambe umhlangano wekukhuluma ngentfutfuko yetinsita temmango kanye netinkinga letibhekene nekuphila kwansuku tonkhe. Kukhulunywe kakhulu ngekuntuleka kwemanti, tinkinga tetindlu, kanye nekubambezeleka kwetinsita letitsintsa bantfu ngco. Tikhulu temasipala tichazile kutsi kunezinhlelo letisachubeka tekuphucula kusebenta kwetinsita. Emiphakatsi itsi kudzingeka kube nekukhuluma lokuchubekako kuze kuncishiswe tinkinga. Uhulumeni utsi kubambisana kubalulekile ekwakheni imiphakatsi lehlala kahle. Lomhlangano uphetse ngemibono lekhombisa isifiso sekubona lushintjo loluhle."}
{"id": 7, "lang": "ss", "domain": "government", "text": "Ngemuva kwemihlangano yavelonkhe, uhulumeni umemetele tinguquko letisha etinhlelweni tekunakekelwa kwetinsita temmango kuze kuncishiswe kubambezeleka ekuphendvuleni tikhalo tebantfu. Lolu hlelo lutawusebentisa tindlela tedijithali kuze kulandzelwe kahle konkhe lokwentekako. Bantfu batawukwati kubona simo setikhalo tabo ngesikhatsi sangempela. Tikhulu titsi loku kutawukhuphula kubeka obala kanye nekutiphendvulela. Emiphakatsi ikhutsatwa kutsi isebentise lolu hlelo olusha kuze kusheshiswe kulungiswa kwetinkinga. Uhulumeni utsi lolu shintjo lutawuphucula kakhulu kusebenta kwetinsita."}
{"id": 8, "lang": "ss", "domain": "municipal_services", "text": "Emadolobheni lamancane aseMpumalanga, umasipala ucale luhlelo lwekukhanyisa imigwaco lobekuvamise kuba mnyama ebusuku. Lolu hlelo lugcile ekufakeni emalambu lamasha langasebentisa mandla lamancane futsi ahlala sikhatsi leside. Tikhulu titsi loku kutawunciphisa tingozi kanye nekukhuphula kuphepha kwemphakatsi. Bantfu bavakalise kujabula ngalomsebenti kepha bacela kutsi uhlanganiswe kahle kuze kufinyelelwe tindzawo tonkhe. Uhulumeni wasekhaya utsi lomsebenti utawuchubeka kuze kuphele tindzawo letibalulekile. Loku kubukwa njengentfutfuko lebalulekile emphakatsini."}
{"id": 9, "lang": "ss", "domain": "government", "text": "Uhulumeni wesifundza umemetele luhlelo lwekukhulisa kufinyelela kwetinsita temmango etindzaweni tasemaphandleni letikhashane nemadolobha. Lolu hlelo lutawugxila ekunikeni emasevisi eliphilo, kufaka emakhliniki, ematfuba emfundo kanye nekuphucula imigwaco. Tikhulu titsi loku kutawunciphisa sidzingo sekutsi bantfu bahambe emabanga lamade kuze batfole lusito. Emiphakatsi itsi iyalwemukela loluhlelo kepha ifuna kube khona kubeka obala ekusetjentisweni kwetinsita. Uhulumeni utsi utawusebentisana netinhlangano temmango kuze kuqinisekiswe kuphumelela kwalomsebenti."}
{"id": 10, "lang": "ss", "domain": "civic_affairs", "text": "Ngaphakathi kwemphakatsi waseGoli, bantfu bahlangene emhlanganweni wekukhuluma ngentfutfuko yetindzawo tabo kanye netinsita letidzingekako. Kukhulunywe kakhulu ngekulungiswa kwemigwaqo, kukhanyisa tindzawo letimnyama, kanye nekuphucula tinsita temanti. Tikhulu tichazile kutsi kunetinhlelo letisachubeka tekuphucula onkhe la masevisi ngekucophelela. Bantfu bakhutsatwa kutsi bahlale babika tinkinga kuze kulungiswa kusheshiswe. Uhulumeni utsi kubambisana kwemphakatsi kubalulekile ekwakheni tindzawo letihlala kahle. Lomhlangano uphetse ngemoya wekusebenta ndzawonye nekutfutfukisa imphilo yabantfu."}
