{"id": 8,"lang": "ss","domain":"municipal_services","text":"Emadolobheni lamancane nasezindzaweni tasemakhaya, umasipala sewucale luhlelo lwekukhanyisa imigwaco lobekuvamise kuba mnyama ebusuku. Lolu hlelo lugcile ekufakeni emalambu lamasha lasindzisa mandla kagesi futsi ahlala sikhatsi leside. Tikhulu titsi loku kutawunciphisa tingozi kanye nekukhuphula kuphepha kwemphakatsi. Bantfu bavakalise kujabula ngalomsebenti kepha bacela kutsi tindzawo tonkhe tifinyelelwe. Uhulumeni wasekhaya utsi lomsebenti utawuchubeka kancane kancane kuze kuphele tindzawo letibalulekile. Loku kubukwa njengentfutfuko lebalulekile ekuphuculeni imphilo yansuku tonkhe."}
{"id": 1, "lang": "ss", "domain": "farming", "text": "Ngaphezu kwabalimi labangu-4 500 emikhakheni yasemakhaya sebazuza kusekelwa lokukhula kwemphilo yekulima kulelive, lokuhloswe ngayo kucinisa kuvikeleka kwetakudla. Luhlelo lwebutfutfukiso luhlanganisa kuhanjiswa kwembewu lemelako, tifundziso tekulima kanye netinsita tekunisela letincane. Lokuhleleka kwetinsita kusita imindeni lemanyenti kutsi ikhone kukhuphula umkhiqizo wayo ngaphandle kwekuncika kakhulu etimakethe letikhashane. Balimi labasha bakhutsatwa kutsi bangenele emiklamo yekufundziswa lokwentiwa tindvuna temiphakatsi kanye netichwepheshe temhlaba. Lokubambisana kwenta kube lula kutsi lwati lolusha lolusunguliwe lufinyelele kulabo labahlala kude netindzawo temadolobha.\n\nEmikhakheni leminyenti, kutfutfukiswa kwemhlaba kusetjentiswa ngekuhleleka lokucophelela lokuhlonipha imvelo kanye nekugwema kudzilika kwenhlabatsi. Tinhlelo tekusimamisa umhlaba tifaka kufakwa kwemigcobo yemvelo, kushintjiswa kwetilimo kanye nekusetjentiswa kwemitfombo yemanzi ngendlela lehlakaniphile. Lokuhlanganiswa kwetindlela letindzala kanye netintfo letisemtsetfweni kusita ekwakheni umnotfo lomelele emiphakatsini yasemaphandleni. Emakhomiti endzawo asebenta kanye nemiphakatsi kutsi kube nekuphatsa lokutimele ekusetjentisweni kwemalungelo emhlabatsi. Loku kukhombisa kutsi intfutfuko yekulima idzinga kubambisana lokucinile phakathi kwabalimi, imiphakatsi kanye netinhlelo tembuso."}
{"id": 2, "lang": "ss", "domain": "farming", "text": "Emadolobhaneni aseNhlalakahle kanye nasemaphandleni lasedvute, kukhula kwetilimo sekube yinsika yekuphila kwetindlu letinyenti letitsetse emhlabeni wetemvelo. Indzawo lekhulunywa ngayo inemhlaba lovundzile lokhonakalako kutsi usetjentiswe kahle uma kunakekelwa ngendlela lefanele. Tinhlelo tekusekela balimi setilekelele ekwakheni tindlela letisha tekulima letihambisana nesimo selitulu lesishintjako. Imiphakatsi ibambe lichaza ekunakekeleni umhlaba wayo ngekusebentisa tindlela letigcina umswakama kanye nekugwema kuguguleka.\n\nEkhuluma nemadvodza nemakhosikati emikhakheni, bekugcizelelwa kubaluleka kwekufundzisa labasha ngemakhono ekulima lokusimeme. Luhlelo lwekutfutfukiswa kwemapulazi lamancane luhlanganisa kufinyelela emathulusi, imbewu kanye netinsita tekulima letisekelako. Lokuhlelwa kwenta kube nelitsemba lokutsi imiphakatsi ingatfola umnotfo locinile ngekusebentisa umhlaba wayo ngendlela lehlakaniphile. Tindvuna temphakatsi tisebenta ngekubambisana netichwepheshe kutfola tindlela letisebenta kahle kakhulu. Loku kukhombisa kutsi intfutfuko yasemakhaya idinga kusebenta ndzawonye nekuphatsa kahle tintfo letikhona."}
{"id": 3, "lang": "ss", "domain": "farming", "text": "Abahlali baseMabhokisini nasemikhakheni lekhona edvute nezigodzi batse balokhu babhekene netinsita letingenele tekusekela kulima kwabo kwansuku tonkhe. Lokushoda kwetinsita kufaka ekhatsi imbewu, emanti kanye nemishini lokusita ekukhuliseni tilimo ngendlela lesimeme. Noma kunjalo, imiphakatsi seyivukile yekubambisana kutfola tindlela tekucinisekisa kutsi umhlaba uyasetjentiswa ngendlela lefanele. Balimi labancane bakhombisa umoya wekusebenta ngekutimisela ngisho nangabe banetinsita letincane.\n\nTichwepheshe temhlaba kanye nemphakatsi sebacale kutfutfukisa tifundziso letigcizelela kugcinwa kwemvelo kanye nekusetjentiswa kahle kwetinsita temvelo. Kukhona netinhlelo tekubolekisa ngemathulusi ekulima letisita kakhulu labo labangenalo litfuba lekutithenga. Lokubambisana kwenta kube nelitsemba lekutsi umnotfo wemakhaya ungakhula kancane kancane. Imihlangano yemphakatsi iyachubeka kutsi kubhekwe tinkinga tekulima kanye netindlela tekutiniketa. Loku kubeka sisekelo sekutsi kulima kube ngumtfombo losemtimbeni wemphilo."}
{"id": 4, "lang": "ss", "domain": "farming", "text": "Izindlela tekulima letingagcini kahle sebetibe yinkinga lekhulako emikhakheni leminyenti yasemaphandleni, lokuholela ekuncipheni kwemkhiqizo kanye nekulahlekelwa ngumhlaba lovundzile. Kuguguleka kwenhlabatsi kanye nekusetjentiswa kabi kwawo kudale kutsi tilimo tingakhuli ngendlela lelisetulu. Imiphakatsi seyicelile kusekelwa lokwengeziwe ekufundzisweni kwetindlela tekulima letigcina umhlaba. Kukhona nesidzingo lesikhulu sekufundzisa balimi ngendlela yekushintja tilimo kute kugcinwe kuvundza kwenhlabatsi.\n\nTinhlelo letisha setifake kugcizelela kubaluleka kwekusetjentiswa kwemanzi ngendlela lehlakaniphile kanye nekulondvolota tindzawo letihlala tiluhlata. Imiphakatsi isebenta netichwepheshe kutsi kufundziswe tindlela tekusebentisa imithombo yemandla ngendlela leyonga imvelo. Lokubambisana kusita ekwakheni tindlela letisimeme tekulima letingakhona kumelana netingucuko tesimo selitulu. Balimi bayakhutsatwa kutsi basebentise lwati lolusha kute bente umhlaba wabo ube nemphumelelo lesimeme. Loku kubeka sisekelo sekutsi kulima kube ngumsebenti lokhula njalo."}
{"id": 5, "lang": "ss", "domain": "farming", "text": "Ngemuva kwekucalwa kweluhlelo lolusha lwebutfutfukiso bemapulazi lamancane, imiphakatsi leminyenti seyibone kukhula kwetilimo kanye nekutfolakala kwetakudla letincono. Lomkhankhaso uhlose kusita balimi labancane ngekutfola imbewu lemelako, tifundziso kanye netinsita tekunisela. Emakhaya lamanyenti akhombisa intfutfuko ngekutsi tilimo tabo seticala kuletsa inzuzo lokhulu kakhulu. Lokuhlanganyela kwemiphakatsi kwenta kube nelitsemba lekutsi umnotfo wendzawo utawuciniswa.\n\nEmihlanganweni yakamuva, bekugcizelelwa kubaluleka kwekusebentisa tindlela tekulima letihambisana nemvelo kanye nekugwema kulimala kwemithombo yemvelo. Tichwepheshe betemhlaba batse batilekelela ekuniketeni lwati lolusha kulabo labasandza kungena ekulimeni. Luhlelo luphindze lwagcizelela kubaluleka kwekusebentisa emathulusi lesimanjemanje ngendlela lekhaliphile. Lokuhlangana kwemiphakatsi kanye netichwepheshe kubalulekile ekuphumeleleni kwetinhlelo tekulima. Loku kukhombisa kutsi intfutfuko yendzawo yakhiwa ngekubambisana."}
{"id": 6, "lang": "ss", "domain": "farming", "text": "Ekhuluma emhlanganweni wemphakatsi waseSigodini saMhlabeni, tindvuna temasimu tichaze kubaluleka kwekucinisekisa kutsi umhlaba usetjentiswa ngendlela lesimeme kute kugcinwe kuvundza kwawo. Bekugcizelelwa kutsi balimi kufanele basebentise tindlela letigcina imvelo kanye nekunciphisa kuguguleka kwenhlabatsi. Loku kufaka ekhatsi kushintja tilimo kanye nekusetjentiswa kwetintfo temvelo letisekelako ekulondvoloteni umhlaba. Imiphakatsi ivumelene kutsi kudzingeka kusebenta lokuhlanganyelako ekulawuleni tindlela tekulima.\n\nTichwepheshe betemvelo batfutfukisa tifundziso letigcizelela kubaluleka kwemanzi kanye nekusetjentiswa kwawo ngendlela lehlakaniphile. Balimi bakhutsatwa kutsi basebentise lwati lolusha lolutfolakala ngemihlangano kanye netifundvo temkhakha wetekulima. Luhlelo luphindze lwakhombisa kutsi intfutfuko yasemakhaya idinga kusekelwa lokucinile kusukela emikhakheni yembuso kanye nemiphakatsi. Lokubambisana kwenta kube nelitsemba lekutsi kulima kungaba ngumtfombo lokhula njalo wemnotfo wemakhaya. Loku kugcizelela kutsi kutfutfukiswa kwemhlaba kudinga kubambisana kanye nekutiphatsa kahle."}
{"id": 7, "lang": "ss", "domain": "farming", "text": "Ngaphezulu kwabalimi labangu-6 000 basebentisa tindlela letisha tekulima letisekelwa ngemiklamo yekutfutfukisa temapulazi emakhaya, lokuletse kukhula kwemkhiqizo wetilimo emkhatsini wemiphakatsi leminyenti. Lokukhula kukhombisa imphumelelo yetinhlelo tekufundzisa kanye nekusita balimi ngemathulusi kanye nembewu lemelako. Imiphakatsi ibika kutsi kunekwehla kwekushoda kwetakudla ngenca yekutsi tilimo setikhula ngendlela lesimeme. Lokubambisana kwenta kube nelitsemba lekutsi tindzawo tasemakhaya tingaba nemnotfo locinile.\n\nTinhlelo letichubekako tigcizelela kubaluleka kwekusebentisa umhlaba ngendlela lehlakaniphile kanye nekugwema kuguguleka kwawo. Balimi labasha bayakhutsatwa kutsi bangenele tifundziso letinika lwati lolujulile ngemakhono ekulima. Tichwepheshe batfutfukisa tindlela letingasita ekwandiseni umkhiqizo ngaphandle kwekulimata imvelo. Lokubambisana kwemiphakatsi kanye netichwepheshe kwenta kube nelitsemba lekutsi kulima kungachubeka kukhula. Loku kukhombisa kutsi intfutfuko yasemaphandleni isekelwe ekubambisaneni."}
{"id": 8, "lang": "ss", "domain": "farming", "text": "Emaphandleni aseMhlabeni Omusha, balimi sebabone intfutfuko ngekukhula kwetilimo kanye nekutfolakala kwetinsita tekulima letisekelako. Imikhakha lemisha yekusekela balimi iletse litfuba lekutsi imindeni ikhone kukhuphula umnotfo wayo ngekulima. Tinhlelo tekufundzisa setihlanganise tindlela tekulima letihambisana nesimo selitulu kanye nekugcinwa kwemvelo. Lokuhlelwa kwetinsita kwenta kube lula kutsi balimi batfole lusito ngesikhatsi lesidingekile.\n\nImiphakatsi ibambisene netindvuna temasimu kanye netichwepheshe ekutfutfukiseni tindlela tekulima letisebenta kahle. Kugcizelelwa kubaluleka kwekusetjentiswa kwemanzi ngendlela lehlakaniphile kanye nekugwema kuguguleka kwenhlabatsi. Balimi bakhutsatwa kutsi basebentise tindlela letinsha tekushintja tilimo kute kugcinwe kuvundza kwemhlaba. Lokubambisana kusita ekwakheni umnotfo wendzawo lokhula kancane kancane. Loku kukhombisa kutsi intfutfuko yasemakhaya idinga kusebenta ndzawonye."}
{"id": 9, "lang": "ss", "domain": "farming", "text": "Abahlali baseLuphongolo nasezindzaweni letibomakhelwane bakhombisa intfutfuko ngenca yetinhlelo tekusekela kulima lokwentiwa ngemphakatsi kanye nemkhakha wemnotfo wemakhaya. Balimi labancane batfola lusito ngemathulusi ekulima, imbewu kanye netifundziso letibasita kukhuphula umkhiqizo wabo. Lokubambisana kwenta kube nelitsemba lekutsi tindzawo tasemakhaya tingakhula emnotfweni. Imiphakatsi iyakhutsatwa kutsi ibambe lichaza ekunakekeleni umhlaba wayo.\n\nTichwepheshe betemhlaba batfutfukisa tifundziso letigcizelela kubaluleka kwekusetjentiswa kwemanzi kanye nekugwema kulimata imvelo. Balimi bayafundziswa kutsi bashintje tilimo ngendlela lehlakaniphile kute kugcinwe kuvundza kwenhlabatsi. Luhlelo luphindze lwagcizelela kubaluleka kwekusebentisa lwati lolusha ekukhuliseni umnotfo wemakhaya. Lokubambisana kwemiphakatsi kanye netichwepheshe kwenta kube nelitsemba lekutsi kulima kungachubeka kukhula. Loku kukhombisa kutsi intfutfuko yakhiwa ngekubambisana lokucinile."}
{"id": 10, "lang": "ss", "domain": "farming", "text": "Izinkinga tekushoda kwemanzi kanye nekuguguleka kwenhlabatsi setibe yinsita lenkhulu etindzaweni letinyenti tasemaphandleni, lokudinga kutsi kubekwe tindlela letisha tekulima letisimeme. Imiphakatsi seyicelile kusekelwa lokwengeziwe ekwakheni tindlela tekunisela kanye nekulondvolota imithombo yemvelo. Balimi bakhutsatwa kutsi basebentise tindlela letigcina umswakama wenhlabatsi kanye nekunciphisa kulahleka kwemithombo yemvelo. Lokubambisana kusita ekwakheni tindlela letingamelana netingucuko tesimo selitulu.\n\nTichwepheshe batfutfukisa tifundziso letigcizelela kubaluleka kwekusetjentiswa kwemanzi ngendlela lehlakaniphile kanye nekushintja tilimo njalo. Luhlelo luphindze lugcizelele kubaluleka kwekusebentisa emathulusi lesimanjemanje ngendlela lengalimati imvelo. Imiphakatsi kanye netindvuna temasimu basebenta ndzawonye kute bakhe umnotfo wemakhaya losimeme. Balimi bayakhutsatwa kutsi basebentise lwati lolusha kute bakhuphule umkhiqizo wabo. Loku kukhombisa kutsi intfutfuko yasemakhaya idinga kusebenta lokuhlanganyelako."}
{"id": 1, "lang": "ss", "domain": "farming", "text": "Emasimu aseSigodini saseNdlovukazi sekubikwe kukhula lokubonakalako kwemikhiqizo yetilimo ngemuva kwekutfola kusekelwa lokusha lokuhloswe ekucinisiseni kuphepha kwetakudla. Imindeni lebalimi isitsite kutsi imbewu lehanjiswa ngemalanga lamuva isite kakhulu ekwandiseni kuvuna kwabo. Lokubambisana phakathi kwetindvuna temphakatsi netichwepheshe betekulima sekubeke sisekelo sekusetjentiswa kahle kwemhlaba. Balimi bakhutsatwa kutsi basebentise tindlela tekushintja tilimo kute kugcinwe kuvundza kwenhlabatsi. Loku kusita ekunciphiseni kuguguleka kanye nekugcina imvelo yendzawo.\n\nKulelikhaya, tinkhundla tekufundzisa balimi setibambe indzima lenkhulu ekutfutfukiseni lwati lolusha. Tifundziso tigcizelela kubaluleka kwekusetjentiswa kwemanzi ngendlela lehlakaniphile kanye nekugwema kulahleka kwemithombo yemvelo. Imiphakatsi isebenta ndzawonye kucinisa emakhono ebantfu labasha labangena ekulimeni. Lokubambisana kulekelela ekwakheni umnotfo lomelele emikhakheni yasemakhaya. Lokukhula kukhombisa kutsi kulima kungaba ngumtfombo lomkhulu wemphilo lesimeme uma kulawulwa kahle."}
{"id": 2, "lang": "ss", "domain": "farming", "text": "Emakhaya aseMhlabeni Wekudla sekubikwe tinguquko letinhle ekusetjentisweni kwemhlaba lolimekako ngemuva kwekucalwa kwetinhlelo tekusekela balimi labancane. Imindeni leminyenti isitsite kutsi seyitfola lusito ngemathulusi ekulima kanye nemathuba ekufundza tindlela letinsha tekukhulisa tilimo. Lokubambisana kwemiphakatsi netindvuna temasimu sekutsite kwenta kube nelitsemba lekutsi umnotfo wemakhaya utawuchubeka ukhula. Balimi bakhutsatwa kutsi basebentise imithombo yemandla ngendlela lengalimati imvelo.\n\nTichwepheshe betemhlaba bagcizelela kubaluleka kwekugcina kuvundza kwenhlabatsi ngekushintja tilimo kanye nekusetjentiswa kwetindlela tekunisela letonga emanti. Imihlangano yemphakatsi isebenta njengendzawo yekwabelana lwati kanye nekucinisekisa kutsi konkhe lokwentiwako kuhambisana netidzingo temvelo. Loku kubeka sisekelo sekutsi kulima kube ngumsebenti lokhula njalo futsi longatfutfuki kuphela kepha futhi losimeme."}
